# Phase gates

See `docs/DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md` and `docs/DECISIONS.md`.

## Phase 0

Tree, MIT LICENSE, pyproject (`~=` deps), schema, `.gitignore`, CI (pytest + ruff), examples, server skeleton with `/mcp` SSE stub.

## Phase 1

Read-only MCP, poller, WS `snapshot_update`, ServerGrid. Anomaly logged only — **no agent**. Bind `127.0.0.1`.

**Done when:** live metrics from `droplet`/`linode` after Q7 paths filled.

## Phase 2

Agent one-shot JSON, incident tools (correlate without GitHub), ApprovalCard, MCP approve (not HIGH), LOW auto-exec on `test-nginx`, `action_pending_reminder`.

**Done when:** kill `test-nginx` → approval or auto-restart; `primary DB` never touched.

## Phase 3

Execution tools incl. `run_ssh_command`; ExecutionLog; health fail → new incident. **No** `rollback_deployment` yet.

## Phase 4

`repos.yaml`, cicd tools, correlate + GitHub, `rollback_deployment`, postmortem, handoff drawer, recharts sparklines, false_positive UI.

## Phase 5 (not started in repo)

Terraform MCP (read/plan; apply gated). Spec in `docs/PHASES_5_9_PLAN.md` (local, gitignored).

## Phase 6

`compliance.py`, sensitive-service gates, `compliance_audit_log`, dashboard `COMPLIANCE` ack, MCP `get_compliance_context` / `list_compliance_audit`. See `docs/DECISIONS.md`.
